---
import Link from "./ui/link.astro";
---

<div
  class="bg-slate-900 p-8 md:px-20 md:py-20 mt-20 mx-auto max-w-5xl rounded-2xl flex flex-col items-center text-center shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/10">
  <h2 class="text-white text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight max-w-2xl leading-tight">
    Tugas Selesai Tepat Waktu atau Uang Kembali!
  </h2>
  <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4 text-base md:text-lg max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
    Dapatkan jaminan pengerjaan sesuai deadline, lolos uji Turnitin, privasi identitas aman 100%, dan gratis revisi sampai tuntas. Jangan pertaruhkan nilai akademismu, konsultasikan sekarang.
  </p>
  <div class="flex mt-6 w-full sm:w-auto justify-center">
    <Link 
      href="https://wa.me/6283153512049?text=Halo%20Admin%20SiPintar,%20saya%20mau%20konsultasi%20mengenai%20garansi%20dan%20order%20tugas..." 
      target="_blank"
      style="inverted"
      class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-3 text-center font-medium bg-white text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-100 transition rounded-lg">
      Pesan Sekarang (WA)
